      "date": "2017-12-16 17:58:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nTwo requests then:\n- test if this improves DoM performance for small writes.  It should remove one RTT for a write\n- add some sanity tests to verify that this feature is being used (if server version supports it), so that it doesn’t accidentally break, but we don’t notice it because regular RDMA is used.",
