      "date": "2017-12-17 08:30:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAndreas, I am not sure about 1) - this is always enabled so what's the point of checking that if we cannot choose anyway.\nAs for 2) I am not sure how to check that, do we have any counters in stats for bulks? So far I can propose just check lustre debug log for related messages \"short io is used\" which is not so reliable for tests. Any proposals how to check was there bulk or not?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
